   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Ninety-nine GOD IS LIGHT AND GOD IS LOVE Scripture: 1 John 1:5; 4:8 God is light Light is a matter of nature.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Light has the function of shining.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>God as light denotes the function of that nature of God which is shining.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Once man touches God, he receives light.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>He is no more in darkness.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>God is love Love is a matter of sentiment.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Love has the function of imparting warmth.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>God as love denotes the function of the sentiment of God which imparts warmth.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Once man touches God, he receives warmth and departs from coldness.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>How God is expressed as light and love He shows forth His light in His Son Jesus.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>He shows forth His love through the cross.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>God caused His Son to accomplish redemption through the cross to become man s Savior, that man may obtain Him as light and love.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>How to obtain God as light and love Confess that you are in darkness and in coldness.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Receive the Son of God, Jesus Christ, as your Savior.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Have fellowship with God through Christ.</S>
   </TEXT>
